Program: Outlook
Title: Racism in Russia
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrtx
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Racism in Russia, a look at racist attacks on foreign students in Russian university towns and 'friendship lessons' which explain foreign cultures to Russian students. Also, prejudice - social psycologist Arthur Cassidy discusses what causes it; interpreting dreams; photographer Dave Hogan on taking better photographs. Show less